  "history": "The client spent about a year working on a project in Europe, building a website and conducting interviews, which they feel proud of and wish to share. They have a history of procrastination and anxiety, and currently use strategies learned from a course and reminders to manage daily life. The client is now facing ambiguity about their life direction and choices, with many options to consider. Their pride in past accomplishments contrasts with current uncertainty, which may challenge their confidence and self-efficacy.",
